<br>
The only thing that can do some good is to write and call.  The committee members view this as a small issue and not important.  People need to convince them otherwise.<br>
<br>
The advice of just writing you own senators should be ignored.  Everybody needs to write Hatch and Leahy whether you are their state or not.  The bill is coming up Thursday morning and nobody expects them to postpone it again.<br>
<br>
Time is running out!!!<br>
<br>
You can repost this anywhere.<br>
<br>
John Wickman<br>
